    "DisplayTitle": "Wildlife Control: [Creature]",
    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nmicroTech Protection Services need a professional to bring the number of ~mission(Creature) in the wild back to within acceptable parameters. Their population is increasing too quickly, and culling some of their numbers will help ensure the situation doesn\u2019t spiral out of control.\n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation.\n\u2022 Locate the ~mission(Creature) on ~mission(Location).\n\u2022 Use force as necessary to eliminate the ~mission(Creature).\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 1 year of relevant mercenary and/or security experience.\n\u2022 Access to combat equipment.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Experience with extermination\n\nFor more information on the animals in question, refer to \"The Guide to Stanton Wildlife\" in your Journal.",
